data.description: Showings start Sat - Gorgeous Millard home has been beautifully updated with a sweeping park view. So much room to run, play, walk the dogs with this huge neighborhood park as an extension of the backyard. Kitchen, dining, primary bedroom and the huge deck all have 24/7 park views. Most importantly, no projects to tackle - totally updated home is turnkey and move in ready. All new designer paint colors, lighting, flooring with kitchen and bath updates as well. Kitchen has updated cabinetry and hardware with new quartz countertops and timeless subway backsplash. Primary bedroom with new carpet, lighting and a beautiful updated ensuite bath with walk-in shower. Lower level is finished with new paint and carpet as well. Close to Chalco Hills Recreation Area and Wehrspann Lake. Just seconds to the interstate. So convenient! Pre-inspected by Corspect. Open Sun 1-3.
